I learn from the sheep every day.\
Their friendly, gentle quiet ways, observing, trusting, and communicating about their needs. \
It is special seeing ewes birthing, and caring for the lambs.\
The sheep and geese are never in the same pen, so this display of affection was amazing.\
\
Sheep graze all around our property. \uc0\u8232 They are our solar lawnmowers!\
